{"tid":1916590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際戰線「捉鬼撚」又炮打Luke de Pulford","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T04:53:49.000Z","uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d529142204693fbf9a59ebb8ec4d87f59517875f","tid":1916590,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"呢班人好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joey.siu.90/posts/1681161092024225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoey.siu.90%2Fposts%2F1681161092024225&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=be750949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joey.siu.90/posts/1681161092024225</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/H8oT2TN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8oT2TN.jpg&h=19129827&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nJoey Siu<br />\n&middot; 2月23日 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n【大佬，Twitter戰線唔是咁玩的】<br />\n<br />\n玩開Twitter嘅手足應該多多少少都見過一堆人，周圍喺外國政要啲tweets下面留言話呢個係鬼嗰個又係鬼，唔好比佢呃、甚至有啲直頭開聲鬧人做乜要見阿邊個邊個咁。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢，首先人地無義務幫香港爭取權益之餘仲要解決埋內部鬥爭；再者咪當人地傻嘅先得架，香港人點解唔再信泛民、本土主義開始成為主流、越嚟越多香港人嗌獨立呢啲你以為人地真係完全無聽過咩。<br />\n<br />\n想盡量傳達呢啲信息咪好聲好氣留言囉，唔使下下口出惡言架喎。<strong>啲議員見HOCC又話佢係左膠唔見得、Solomon見郭榮鏗又群起而攻之比你地鬧到上天花板、今次Luke見咗劉慧卿影咗張相又比你地洗晒版咁。<br />\n<br />\n比你地煩到要特登覆你解釋，真係唔講以為啲外國朋友有份賣香港。再講，你以為鬧完人地就會轉而見你個Dr WC咩。</strong><br />\n<br />\n好心戴返口罩，講少兩句啦。<br />\n<br />\n閱讀智商門檻：IQ87"},{"pid":"c9c7eb0130e1f4f803bbde21723a01b621d43bfb","tid":1916590,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"Luke de Pulford回應原link<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1230629018665472000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1230629018665472000&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=ff0d1e44\" data-ef-url=\"https